  "body": "Currently, `Delete` in task grpc api only takes effect when task is in `stopped` state, and [Task client `Delete`](https://github.com/containerd/containerd/blob/master/task.go#L194) is using the grpc api directly.\r\n\r\nHowever, it seems that we are not aware of this when using the client, e.g. [here](https://github.com/containerd/containerd/blob/master/cmd/ctr/run.go#L128).\r\n\r\nIt seems useful to add an option in the client to forcibly kill and delete the task, especially useful when cleanup.",
